<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>ServiceNow Highlights</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="/search.js"></script>
    <link href="index.css"  rel="stylesheet" >
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    h1, h2, h3 {
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 40px 0 20px;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 0 40px 60px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content-item {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 20px;
      border-left: 2px solid #ddd;
    }

    .content-item::before {
      content: '⬤';
      color: #f4a261;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      position: absolute;
      left: -10px;
      top: 4px;
    }

    .content-item h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #333;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(244, 162, 97, 0.2);
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .content-item p, .content-item ul {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .content-item ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .content-item ul li::before {
      content: "›";
      color: #f4a261;
      margin-right: 6px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .content-grid {
        padding: 0 20px 40px;
      }
      .section-header{
        padding-top: 10%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
 <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  <h1 class="section-header">AI-Powered ServiceNow Excellence</h1>

  <div class="content-grid">

    <div class="content-item">
      <h3>Implementation</h3>
      <p>Deploy ITSM, ITOM, and HRSD rapidly using our structured approach with automation-first configurations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-item">
      <h3>End-to-End Coverage</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>ITSM, HRSD, CSM, SecOps</li>
        <li>Integrations with Salesforce, SAP, Boomi</li>
        <li>Governance & Compliance (GRC)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-item">
      <h3>AI & Automation</h3>
      <p>Embed AI across workflows—predict incidents, auto-resolve tickets, and drive efficiency with machine learning insights.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-item">
      <h3>Support Model</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>24x5 shared service desk</li>
        <li>Real-time monitoring with alerts</li>
        <li>Continuous enhancement cycles</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-item">
      <h3>Client Impact</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>40% faster service delivery</li>
        <li>50% drop in ticket resolution time</li>
        <li>HR case automation for 3,000+ employees</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-item">
  <h3>Engage with Us</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Book a Consultation</strong> – Talk to our ServiceNow experts</li>
    <li><strong>Download Whitepaper</strong> – Best practices & success metrics</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
    <a href="#consultation"
       class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-sm text-white bg-[#f4a261] hover:bg-[#e67e22] transition duration-300 ease-in-out rounded-full shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
       <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check mr-2"></i> Book a Consultation
    </a>

    <a href="#whitepaper"
       class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-2.5 font-medium text-sm text-[#f4a261] border border-[#f4a261] hover:bg-[#f4a261]/10 transition duration-300 ease-in-out rounded-full shadow-sm">
       <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines mr-2"></i> Download Whitepaper
    </a>
  </div>
</div>


  </div>

</body>
</html>
